title: Oakley Offshoot Mens Sunglasses Overview
description:
Oakley Polarized Black Iridium Offshoot Sunglasses - OO9190-05- http://www.abt.com/product/69015/Oakley-OO919001.html

Features
• Frame
o Durable frame of lightweight O Matter engineered for a comfortable fit on larger faces
o Unique metal bands at hinges and stem tips
o Metal icon accents
• Lenses
o Polaric Ellipsoid lens geometry that extends clarity to the edge of a wide peripheral view
o Lens curvature that enhances side protection against sun wind and impact
o Protection of Plutonite lens material that filters out 100 of all UVA UVB UVC and harmful blue light up to 400nm
